###########################################################################
#  eq_nested_supsub - an @Eq expression with sub/super nested several     #
#  layers deep, exercising recursive script box construction in z45.c.    #
###########################################################################

@SysInclude { eq }
@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
Nested scripts (sub inside sup inside sub):
@DP
@CentredDisplay @Eq {
   x sub { i sup { j sub { k sup l } } } = y sup { m sub { n sup o } }
}
@DP
Tower with mixed scripts:
@DP
@CentredDisplay @Eq {
   a sup { b sup { c sup { d sup e } } } + p sub { q sub { r sub { s sub t } } }
}
@End @Text
